net.cloud.mmo.event.command.parameter

Class OptionalParameter<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.mmo.event.command.parameter.CommandParameter<V>
      • net.cloud.mmo.event.command.parameter.OptionalParameter<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The type of the value

    public class OptionalParameter<V>
extends CommandParameter<V>
    A parameter that a command does not required - it may or may not be provided. Has two names associated with it, one of which is needed. Also has a value.
